description: At Get Saunced we love to make and eat really tasty food.We are a team of Chefs who formed this company to bring high-end, scratch made food to the street level. We are taking our fine dinning training and expertise and applying them to the food we are bringing to you. We will be on local streets, The Minneapolis Parks and various festivals operating the "GET SAUCED FOOD TRUCK", "GEORGE'S DOG HOUSE". Come "GET SAUCED"!!Our mission is to bring high-end, scratch made food to the streets using organic, all natural, locally grown, sustainable and environmentally friendly products whenever possible.Awards: Serving Minnesota State Fair BLUE ribbon winning Get Sauced BBQ. Pints available on the truck.
name: Get Sauced
